OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,FScotland's migration minister has
OL,7,Furged the Government to expand the
OL,8,Fnumber of Palestinian people who can
OL,9,Fjoin their family in the UK.
OL,11,FIn a letter to UK minister Tom
OL,12,FPursglove, Emma Roddick pushed for the
OL,13,FRefugee Family Reunion scheme to
OL,14,Finclude "immediate and extended
OL,15,Ffamily, including parents, children
OL,16,Fover 18, siblings and their children".
OL,18,FThe current system allows only for
OL,19,Fpartners and children under 18 to join
OL,20,Ffamily in the UK.
