OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,FMs Roddick suggested the minister meet
OL,7,Fwith families of people stuck in Gaza
OL,8,Fand hear their "harrowing experiences".
OL,10,FShe also called for the Home Office to
OL,11,Fwaive the need for biometric data to
OL,12,Fbe collected for Gazans looking to
OL,13,Fleave before they arrive in the UK, or
OL,14,Fto transfer those trying to come here
OL,15,Fto a site where they can make an
OL,16,Fapplication under the current system.
