OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,F"The Scottish Government and the
OL,7,FScottish Refugee Council fully support
OL,8,Fthe aims of the Gaza Families Reunited
OL,9,Fcampaign alongside more than 74,000
OL,10,Fpeople who have signed a public
OL,11,Fpetition as well as more than 75
OL,12,Fmigrants' rights organisations and law
OL,13,Ffirms across the UK.
OL,15,F"The campaign calls for a scheme to be
OL,16,Fopened for relatives of all
OL,17,FPalestinians in the UK, not just those
OL,18,Fwith refugee status.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
