OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,F"This should be open to a wider cohort
OL,7,Fof immediate and extended family,
OL,8,Fincluding parents, children over 18,
OL,9,Fsiblings and their children.
OL,11,F"Before replying to this letter, I
OL,12,Fwould like to request that you meet
OL,13,Fwith members of the campaign who would
OL,14,Fbe happy to share some of their
OL,15,Fharrowing experiences with you."
OL,17,FBefore responding to her letter, Ms
OL,18,FRoddick asked that the minister meet
OL,19,Fwith Gaza Families Reunited as she did.
