OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,FShe told the story of Doaa, whom she
OL,7,Fsaid spent six weeks without being
OL,8,Fable to contact her mother, sister and
OL,9,Fchildren, as they made the trip from
OL,10,Fthe north of Gaza to Rafah in the
OL,11,Fsouth of the territory on foot.
OL,13,FShe also spoke of Ramy, who has lost
OL,14,F200 members of his extended family.
