OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,FSince the outbreak of war in Gaza, the
OL,7,Fminister said, she has received
OL,8,F"several hundred" letters from
OL,9,Fresidents asking to come to Scotland
OL,10,Fto seek safety, including one father
OL,11,Fwho wrote six times, whose 11-year-old
OL,12,Fdaughter died due to "a lack of
OL,13,Fspecialist food and medical support".
