OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,F"Acting now to provide a temporary
OL,7,Fplace of sanctuary for Gazans with
OL,8,Ffamily in the UK will not only save
OL,9,Flives but is fully aligned with the
OL,10,FUK's responsibility to protect
OL,11,Fcivilians and provide humanitarian
OL,12,Fassistance to those in need," the
OL,13,Fminister said.
OL,15,FMs Roddick also pushed for protections
OL,16,Ffor human rights defenders in the
OL,17,Fregion, including where necessary by
OL,18,Ffacilitating their relocation to the
OL,19,FUK, as part of the UK's overall
OL,20,Fresponse to the current crisis", she
OL,21,Fsaid.
