OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the UK Government
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are working around the clock
OL,8,Fto get British nationals, who want to
OL,9,Fleave, out of Gaza. We have a team on
OL,10,Fthe ground in Cairo and at the Rafah
OL,11,Fcrossing providing consular assistance.
OL,13,F"We currently have no plans to
OL,14,Festablish a separate route for
OL,15,FPalestinians to come to the UK.
OL,16,FHowever, any dependants of British
OL,17,Fcitizens who need a visa, can apply
OL,18,Ffor one."
