OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Gaza Families
OL,7,FReunited campaign said they were
OL,8,F"pleased" Ms Roddick was pushing for
OL,9,Faction.
OL,11,F"We all have a right to family unity
OL,12,Fbut the UK Government's reluctance to
OL,13,Fcreate a Gaza Family Scheme is
OL,14,Fendangering the lives of Palestinians
OL,15,Fin Gaza and keeping families apart,"
OL,16,Fthey added.
OL,18,F"In response to calls for family visa
OL,19,Fschemes for Palestinians from Gaza,
OL,20,Fthe UK Government has signposted to
OL,21,Fexisting routes.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]sD@AOUwD@dO]zD@AOU
