OL,3,CScottish minister calls on UK to allow
OL,4,Cmore Palestinians to join family here
OL,6,F"The British Government has previously
OL,7,Foffered sanctuary to Ukrainian
OL,8,Ffamilies under the Ukraine Family
OL,9,FScheme. All we are asking is that the
OL,10,Fsame option is afforded to
OL,11,FPalestinians seeking protection from
OL,12,Fbombardment and starvation, who want
OL,13,Fto reunite with their loved ones."
